  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients with refractory epilepsy who are candidates for a treatment with vagus nerve
      stimulation will be prospectively randomized into 3 arms with different vagus nerve
      stimulation paradigms. Vagus nerve stimulation parameters are programmed and adjusted during
      outpatient clinic visits, within the normal clinical practice.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
